'''Jean-Baptiste Bagaza''' (* 29.09.1946, [[Rwanda-Urundi|Urundi]] bw’epfo), umukuru w'igihugu ca [[Uburundi]] (1976—1987).

'''Jean-Baptiste Bagaza''' (29.09.1946 - 4.6.2016)  yari Burundi umunyapolitiki wari Perezida wa Njyanama Revolutionary rw'Ikirenga mu Burundi kugeza 10 Ugushyingo, 1976, na Perezida mu Ugushyingo 10, 1976 Nzeri 3 , 1987. Igihe Bagaza yagendaga mu mahanga, yavanywe mu butegetsi bwa gisirikare .  Yasimbuwe na perezida na Pierre Buyoya , ajya mu buhungiro muri Uganda nyuma ajya muri Libiya ,  aho yabaga kugeza mu 1993.
